d from the central black hole, the radio : X-ray correlation\nduring the declining phase is also consistent with core jet emission coupled to\na radiatively efficient accretion flow.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Jan 2018 19:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-24"}
