le of a material with Weyl points, large\nanomalous Hall effect and angle despite a vanishing net magnetic moment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jan 2018 08:52:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Feb 2018 16:23:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 24 Sep 2018 08:31:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-25"}
