 an analytical study of the wavematching of Dirac\nstates and tight binding model calculations, and we analyse in detail the\ndependence of the delamination spectrum on electrostatic conditions in the\nstructure, such as the vertical displacement field.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jan 2018 11:50:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-18"}
